						<div class="postbody">Open bus looks like a solid region of memory filled with the bank byte (in this program).<br /><br />(i.e. reading from $6F0000 on your 1A3B-equivalent should show 512 bytes of $6F, and if the RAM works, you should see something other than 512 bytes of $70 at $700000)</div>

