				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Game is saving now!<br /><br />I connected a 100k resistor between SRAM VCC and CE line as well as connecting 100k + 1N4148 between Batttery+ and SRAM VCC and an additional 1N4148 from VCC to SRAM VCC.<br />SRAM +CE is connected to VCC<br />SRAM /OE is connected to Cart #23<br /><br />All ICs got a 100nF capacitor as well.</div>

